SIMPLE: dreadless
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dreadless
<hw>Dread"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Free from dread;
fearless; intrepid; dauntless; <as>as, <ex>dreadless</ex>
heart</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>dreadless</xex> angel.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Exempt from danger which causes dread; secure.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧ safe in his <xex>dreadless</xex> den.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dreadless</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Dreadless
<hw>Dread"less</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Without doubt.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dreadlessness</ent>⟦br⟧
